{"tid":348890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭下藥塞行李箱！　20歲女模被「黑死組織」放上暗網拍賣","createTime":"2017-08-06T06:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T11:59:28.000Z","uid":108249,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0440e03d02fee78786c48b6c36d9f52ca0de3a","tid":348890,"uid":108249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n英國一名20歲女模特兒抵達義大利米蘭準備參加面試，卻遭到下藥並監禁長達6天，期間更被上手銬放在行李箱中移動，嫌犯將她放上「暗網」拍賣，最後因為她是一名小媽媽，沒有集團願意收下，因此才被釋放。<br />\n<br />\n根據《BBC》報導，這位不具名的20歲模特兒7月10日抵達米蘭，隔天她在經紀公司安排下，前往一處公寓進行拍攝，卻遭到2名男子襲擊，被下藥並上了手銬放進行李箱中，開車帶到杜林（Turin）郊區一處隔離的房子，在房間中被監禁了6天。<br />\n<br />\n嫌犯聲稱為「黑死組織（Black Death Group）」工作，在暗網上面進行拍賣，並且使用加密帳號通知模特兒的經紀公司，勒索30萬美金（約900萬台幣）的贖金，以免女模遭到拍賣，但是之後嫌犯發現女模特兒原來有一名小孩，而他們規定不販賣媽媽，隨即將她載到米蘭的英國大使館釋放。<br />\n<br />\n警方循線調查後，發現嫌犯先前曾舉辦多起網路競標，拍賣遭綁架的女孩，還有詳細的描述與公開的價格，目前依「綁架罪」逮捕了帶女模到大使館的其中一名嫌犯，住在英國的30歲波蘭籍男子赫巴（Lukasz Herba）。受害人受到大使館庇護中。<br />\n<br />\n「暗網（deep web）」是一種必須透過特殊軟體、授權後，才能夠連上的網路，一般的瀏覽器或搜尋引擎都無法找到，且通常都是匿名、無法追蹤的，因此成為許多犯罪者的溫床，上面可以查到各種非法資訊，綁架方法、武器製作、販毒或暗殺等活動，若是不小心闖錯地方，可能哪天會有生命危險也不一定。"},{"pid":"e910b6284baeff9e56aa3ff3c958462b0d678a1d","tid":348890,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"deep web<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e74739ec5c04b3a1f5d29a21da450a2af66a61d","tid":348890,"uid":49144,"like":5,"dislike":48,"score":-43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>deep web<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確嚟講 dark web先啱"},{"pid":"6b450d6a274314034f2f697c8d5e150844798ee9","tid":348890,"uid":6845,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"之後嫌犯發現女模特兒原來有一名小孩，而他們規定不販賣媽媽，隨即將她載到米蘭的英國大使館釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54202e6b7458a462356a6d080b2e323bd882afe9","tid":348890,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"老母唔屌, 屌邊個?"},{"pid":"6d36d80ab9b7278a84fc8e2e252763344e9d8f65","tid":348890,"uid":24457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"諗起救參96小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa690bd7b08a4d64e41cc0adf358a9d47618320","tid":348890,"uid":29609,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fossbytes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Deep-Web-Dark-Web.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffossbytes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FDeep-Web-Dark-Web.jpg&h=eb24ebb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4215ea2d8b1db056f92c69e267dd534370a68b7d","tid":348890,"uid":14130,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://fossbytes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Deep-Web-Dark-Web.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffossbytes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FDeep-Web-Dark-Web.jpg&h=eb24ebb1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n最期待既圖片"},{"pid":"f9d7321eb238f5cef3cda551a3a9b1108a9dadd3","tid":348890,"uid":22566,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://fossbytes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Deep-Web-Dark-Web.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffossbytes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FDeep-Web-Dark-Web.jpg&h=eb24ebb1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n最期待既圖片</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid